snippet.title: Raya Systems promotional VHS video
snippet.description: A promotional VHS video from Raya Systems, maker of health-related educational video games for the Super NES. Includes very brief clips of The AIDS Avenger (unreleased) and a different version of Bronkie the Bronchiasaurus.
